reviews.review_text: Looks like Rain This was my first show and a memorable one.  When you listen to it, you'll hear wild cheers in the middle of songs in places that do not match the lyrics. That's because there was a huge downpour most of the show. The football field was almost a bathtub, and then loud thunder claps. Why they did not call the show us beyond me.  I did not know a lot of Dead songs at the time, but will never forget the place lifting off the ground under the power of the crowd clapping and groovin along with Iko.  Check it out!
